These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower, zinnia, daisy, begonia, amaryllis, poppy
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, green, white, ivory, light-blue, brown, orange
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is not the person who likes brown##6
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who likes green##7
 8. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who likes white##7
10. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
11. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
13. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
14. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
15. the person who growsbegonia is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Flower          | zinnia    | orchid    | balloon-flower | amaryllis | daisy | begonia    | poppy |
| Color   | light-blue | turquise | white  | brown   | ivory    | green | orange |

