.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog, lizard, snake, frog, pony
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, august, october, september, june, december, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in august##7
 6. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 7. the owner of the snake is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
10. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
11. the person who's birthday is in december is not the owner of the pony##6
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Pet    | pony  | hedgehog | frog | lizard | bird     | snake | guinea-pig  |
| Birthday   | october | december | august  | july  | june | september      | november |

