.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, dressmaker, accountant, paramedic, manager, software-developer, lawyer
House: wooden, cape-cod, colonial, cottage, palace, craftsman, gothic-revival
 1. the gothic-revival house is between the accountant and the colonial house##2
 2. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
 3. the cape-cod house is not the paramedic##6
 4. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 5. the wooden house is between the craftsman house and the manager##2
 6. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
 7. the lawyer is on the far right##1
 8. the paramedic is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 9. the accountant is somewhere between the palace house and the gothic-revival house##7
10. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
11. the manager is in an even position##4
12. the manager is not the wooden house##6
13. the software-developer is somewhere between the dressmaker and the manager##7
14. the cottage house is on the left or right of the manager##3
15. the accountant is on the left or right of the manager##3
16. the manager is not the craftsman house##6
17. the paramedic is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
18. the dressmaker is on the right of the librarian##1
19. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
