.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, crime, drama, project-managering, spy, horror, romance
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, photographer, security-guard, project-manager, fisherman, scientist, designer
 1. the designer is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 2. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
 3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
 4. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
 5. the person watching project-managering movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
 6. the scientist is on the right of the photographer##1
 7. the security-guard is somewhere between the photographer and the fisherman##7
 8. the person watching project-managering movies is on the far left##1
 9. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
10. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
11. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person watching crime movies##7
12. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
13. the project-manager is on the left of the coach##1
14. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
15. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
16. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
17. the project-manager is between the person watching horror movies and the scientist##2
18. the person watching spy movies is not the designer##6
19. the coach is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2    |     3     |     4      |     5      |    6    |    7     |
