 4. the teacher is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
 5. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5
 6. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
