 9. the dancer is not the person driving the helicopter##6
10. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5
11. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
12. the person driving the roller is the chef##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
14. the person driving the tram is the accountant##1
15. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
16. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

