 4. the person driving the taxi is the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the fan blues is on the left of the fan funk##1
 6. the fan indie is somewhere between the fan rock and the fan folk##7
 7. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
 8. the fan folk is in an even position##4
 9. the person driving the car is the fan electronic##1
10. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the helicopter and the fan indie##2
11. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
12. the fan indie is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fan rock##1
14. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
15. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
16. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5
