16. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
17. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is chess##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Hobby           | baking | rock-climbing | gardening   | chess | reading | skydiving | dancing |
| Color   | azure     | ebony       | grey | turquise       | blue   | coral | ivory  |

